==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===
* Able to perform OASW at 100 ASW.
* Able to convert between Kai Ni and Kai Ni D remodels.
** Modernisation will be reset on conversion.
* Able to equip Daihatsu and Type 2 Ka-Mi tank at Kai Ni D.

===Overview===
'''Kai'''
* Average firepower, torpedo, ASW, HP and armour.  

'''Kai Ni'''
* Good firepower and torpedo.
* Average ASW, HP and armour.

'''Kai Ni D'''
* Average firepower and HP.
* Good torpedo, ASW and armour.

